body:
Hey guys Zegita here I think a few avicus players know me here from Nebula and from other stuff as well and I just wanted to see if I could get some feedback on my Youtube Channel.

It's hard getting noticed and some people have told me to just stop but I'm not giving up and that's why it would be just amazing just for a few seconds/minutes to check out my channel and give me some feedback.

Here are some of my latest videos:

Trolling with Somali_Captain https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DgiW_Fp-yH8

Avicus Highlights #1 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uRqkzlvYsOQ

Avicus Highlights #2 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XO-lTCyf9xw

Gotta Love Hackers ;) https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uXHeDWSKlkE

Sneaking into the Monument ;) https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6qVoi_DAEbA&feature=youtu.be

If you could just check these out it would very helpful thank you :).

"Zegita or Zeg"
